ingredients.alim_nom_eng: Salt, white (sea, igneous or rock), iodine added, no other enrichment

ingredients_text: cereals (wheat flour (32%) - wholemeal wheat flour (15%), wholemeal rye flour, wholemeal barley flour)- glucose-fruciose syrup - sugar-vegetable fat (palm) - stabiliser: glycerol – glucose syrup - concentrated strawberry puree (strawberry equivalent 2%) - starch - raising agents: ammonium bicarbonate, sodium bicarbonate - salt - dried skimmed milk - acids: citric acid, trisodium citrate - colour: beetroot red-gelling agent: pectin-flavouring - milk solids, may contain traces of nuts and soya,
